Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:06.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:29.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:12.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:34.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:39.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:05.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:32.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their total bounty exceeds 600 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Jolly Roger belongs to the Straw Hat Crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think with your\N120 million bounty, Roronoa Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did you get that Jolly Roger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:38.45,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Mansion in Chaos! An Enraged Don\Nand an Imprisoned Crew"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! But I'm not\Nabout to fall into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have a 300-million-Berry bounty,\Nbut you're nothing before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your yapping!\NGive back our Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can defeat us brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll take you to that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I nearly fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a hard time fighting on the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as tricky for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Arctic Path falls under\Nthe Accino Family's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're in unison, no one here\Nstands a chance against us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, we have the power\Nof magnetism that strongly unites us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, you're doomed\Nto succumb to our brotherly love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough of your boasting.\NJust come at me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick your butts in no time flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, we siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be taking your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you were able to dodge that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get him in one go,\NBig Brother Campaccino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa is growing anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are in perfect unison!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have expected as much\Nfrom a 300-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did a number on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I haven't done anything yet.\NAre you stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate scum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he mock us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:06:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! How dare you get rough\Nwith my Shark Submerge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make you pay\Nfor that, you hockey freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before you turn to ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the bravado up while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks! Where the heck are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, I'm sorry.\NI let my guard down just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks. You're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're down to four bounties left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just knew you were bounty hunters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, dang, this place is freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was carved from layers of ice that\Nhave been forming for hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It quickly freezes anything that is inside.\NYou could say it's a natural freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbell, that comparison was really great!\NIt was super easy to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see whether\Nwe'll catch the other four first
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or you'll freeze first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By now, my children should\Nhave taken out your crewmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity! I hate to slice apart\Nthe guy who treated me to a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:08:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, slice me apart? Are you up to the task?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Devil Fruit power holder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can melt anything I touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could do this to your splendid\Nsword in mere seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gained this ability from my Hot-Hot Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I just can't touch you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-six Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! Are you trying to\Nhurt my beloved collection?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troisième Haché!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong... Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star! Exploding Star Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Hammer! Usopp Rubberband of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star! Pound!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Exploding Star! Exploding Star Star!\N--You're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way out. Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hammer! Exploding Star! Pound!\N--It looks like that is the only way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Exploding Star! Exploding Star!\N--Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I wasn't even able to dent it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Do "that."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I should have enough for one last blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, guys! Everyone ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1.0 Cola Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'm outta cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you got us far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and freeze over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's horrible, Arbell-sama!\ND-Don Accino-sama is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there and wait for the others to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up, Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming, Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:11:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're seriously gonna\Nfreeze if we stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This isn't good!\N--It's like a sauna in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let Papa's mood\Nget any worse! Put on a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you make sure to gather\Nup my birthday presents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Papa! We've gathered them--gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roronoa Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Uh, if I remember right...\N--Hawk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Wave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a mistake that\Nallowed one to slip through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Papa-san, don't worry! We'll be sure\Nto do a perfect job rounding up the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you got a new flag\Nto add to your collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? So cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my brothers-in-law will hunt\Ndown the remaining members!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working. We can't\Nsoothe his temper on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You're tougher than\NI expected, Clone Technique Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you, we're twins!\NListen to what people tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Papa is waiting for us.\NWe need to wrap this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Campaccino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your head is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right.\N--Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't run from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've escaped death\Nfor now, Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finish you off later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Papa has gotten\Neven worse! We have to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you two! Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give back our Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You'll die if you go to sleep!\NWake up, Usopp! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wake me up, Nami.\NI'm in the middle of a pretty dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so many birdies and butterflies...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry, you've come for me, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell have you guys been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we should be asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I saw our flag upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it really is here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta get it back before Luffy notices!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You can't even protect a\Nsingle flag, you lame excuse for a cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back at you! How dare you come back\Nempty-handed, you shitty swordsman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Jerk, take this!\N--Hey, watch where you fling that sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This is no time for fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like everyone is doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Moron.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Pull us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Miss, you're supposed\Nto go down there with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But see, you're special, Big Sister Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Papa to spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Papa does anything I ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go to the birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! It's for Papa!\NWe have a whole bunch of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Say goodbye to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry and rescue us!\N--C'mon! Hurry and save us! Robin!\N--Robin-chan! Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Robin-chan! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we head on up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why'd you leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back like a normal person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to destroy our ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:17:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bit warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it off. It's best to stay away\Nfrom Papa when he gets like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he'll melt everyone around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Let's go play in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's take those snacks and drinks with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so warm, I doubt they'll be very yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. Also, I'd like\Nto ask a favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punks, you've got a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Little Lady Lil's friend, Robin-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A delivery...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan, I always believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Here's some cola, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! You can leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super! Cola replenished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wasted a bunch of time down there,\Nso let's get going, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here, Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't go!\N--Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! If we could raise\Nour Jolly Roger again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd return to your old self!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to bring it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already given up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words "given up" sound so lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't suit you, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man who's supposed\Nto become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the man who will\Nbecome the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still puny and a total weakling,\Nbut just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll steal it back and--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wha--?!\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you whack him, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't exclude me from the conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a cold-hearted brute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt! What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only someone who has fought till the\Nvery end may use the words "given up."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way a guy like this could\Nbecome the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll become\Nthe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided that Puzzle-san\Nis going to become the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up on my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, you aren't weak at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got an inner strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Let's go get our flags back, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive them for\Nstealing our Jolly Rogers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't stand a chance against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to die.\NI'm going to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idiot...! All for me, everyone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:22:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, we're going after Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami! Aren't we in trouble\Nif Zoro is leading the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll turn this into a\Nparty you'll never forget, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cheer up, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give our Jolly Roger back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't drag your feet! Luffy's on his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you he'd come, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a matter of time before we capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I got mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.67,0:23:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you damn moss head!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only followed you since you claimed\Nto know where the Jolly Roger was!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off! Be quiet for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck do we have to follow this jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Phoenix Returns! The Dream\NSworn to Friends on a Jolly Roger"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
